metadata.name: SEA-SIDE  SERENITY
metadata.description:
"SEA-SIDE SERENITY" is a captivating artwork that portrays the tranquil beauty of a coastal landscape. In the foreground of the painting, we see a man walking with his faithful companion, a dog, along a road that runs parallel to the beach. The road is separated from the sandy shore by a sturdy, wired iron fence, which adds a touch of rustic charm to the scene. 
On the beach, we see a man enjoying the soothing ambiance of the sea, lounging under a canopy and beside a small, cozy beach house.
